description:
A dating app for your photos

PhotoSwooper is a dating app for your photos.

Have you ever had too many photos and would just love to swipe them like dating profiles? Well I made just the app: PhotoSwooper. :D


Features:

  • Undo button
  • Info drawer
  • Review screen before photos are deleted
  • Statistics page
  • No ads, forever!

Hope you enjoy!
